Jewel]les replie Partly of such, as he hath slaunderously charg[...] Harding withal: partly of such other, as he h[...] committed about the triall thereof, in the text of the foure first articles of his Replie. By Iohn Latius, at the signe of the Sower, Printed in Antwerpe : 1566. With speciall grace and priuilege.
